        <h3>Steps for Basic Meditation:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Find a quiet space and sit comfortably.</li>
            <li>Close your eyes and focus on your breathing.</li>
            <li>Inhale deeply, exhale slowly.</li>
            <li>Whenever your mind wanders, gently return to your breath.</li>
            <li>Practice for at least 5-10 minutes daily.</li>
